---
title: Chinese Inspired Sweet and Sour Chicken with Pineapple, Pepper and Jasmine Rice
description: This Chinese Inspired Sweet and Sour Chicken is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-inspired-sweet-and-sour-chicken-9945ed7f-c3c33a4c.jpg
